		<title>龐大的政府刺激方案推動中國股市飆升</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/huge-government-stimulus-sends-chinese-stocks-soaring</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 01:44:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市場新聞及觀點]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[CH50]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[China 50]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Indices]]></category>
